{"lastModified":1775541569804,"uri":"c::7646090758::vessel::1f1245b0-6e8d-11ef-80b0-65aca8311de8","yachtType":["Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia\n\n26.11 m sailing yacht BELLKARA, built by Conrad Shipyard, combines performance, comfort, and award-winning custom design. With her aluminium hull and advanced lifting keel, she ensures smooth sailing in various conditions. Her expansive deck areas are perfect for sunbathing, relaxing, or enjoying time with loved ones. Furthermore, her new sails enhance performance, making her a standout choice for those who appreciate advanced sailing technology. Bellkara effortlessly balances innovation with relaxation, offering a truly unique experience on the sea.\n\nBellkara's key features set her apart. First, her award-winning custom design reflects the highest standards of craftsmanship. Next, her spacious guest accommodation ensures comfort throughout the journey. Moreover, her expansive deck areas provide versatile spaces for relaxation and entertainment. Lastly, her advanced sailing technology, including a lifting keel and new sails, offers exceptional performance. Bellkara promises a seamless blend of comfort, style, and cutting-edge sailing capabilities. Bellkara Yacht for Charter is available in Croatia and is located in marina Baotic, Seget Donji, as the Homeport.\n\n","blueprint":{"name":"BELLKARA","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::1f1245b0-6e8d-11ef-80b0-65aca8311de8::assets::69a033b0-21d6-11f0-b5a5-8ba9d9bbcd60/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::1f1245b0-6e8d-11ef-80b0-65aca8311de8::assets::8d651c80-6e8e-11ef-ac91-a3e0671e2668/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::1f1245b0-6e8d-11ef-80b0-65aca8311de8::assets::3969a150-6e8e-11ef-a03e-97ed79e0c361/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::1f1245b0-6e8d-11ef-80b0-65aca8311de8::assets::69c10220-21d6-11f0-b5a5-8ba9d9bbcd60/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::1f1245b0-6e8d-11ef-80b0-65aca8311de8::assets::8d6